We tried to visit you at the hospital...

1231
01:46:18,280 --> 01:46:20,950
试着到医院看你
when we were in New York to pick up Iris...

1232
01:46:21,240 --> 01:46:23,800
那时你还在昏迷中
but you were still in a coma.

