There is no way we can repay you...

1234
01:46:26,360 --> 01:46:29,470
帮我们找回艾瑞丝
for returning our Iris to us.

1235
01:46:29,760 --> 01:46:31,430
我们以为我们失去她了
We thought we had lost her...

1236
01:46:31,640 --> 01:46:34,790
现在我们的生活恢复正常
and now our lives are full again.

1237
01:46:35,320 --> 01:46:36,630
不用多说
Needless to say...

1238
01:46:36,840 --> 01:46:41,350
你是这个家的英雄
you are something of a hero around this household.

1239
01:46:42,120 --> 01:46:45,590
我相信你会想知道艾瑞丝的近况
I'm sure you want to know about Iris.

1240
01:46:45,800 --> 01:46:49,310
她回到学校  非常用功
She's back in school and working hard.

1241
01:46:49,600 --> 01:46:52,630
