The transition has been very hard for her...

1242
01:46:52,840 --> 01:46:54,150
你应该想像得到
as you can well imagine.

1243
01:46:54,320 --> 01:46:55,460
计程车司机英雄康复中

1244
01:46:55,680 --> 01:46:57,190
但我们一步步地慢慢来
But we have taken steps to see...

1245
01:46:57,440 --> 01:47:01,630
不希望她再逃家
she has never cause to run away again.

1246
01:47:02,200 --> 01:47:03,630
简单地来说
In conclusion...

1247
01:47:03,840 --> 01:47:07,590
史提恩斯马太太跟我打从心里
Mrs. Steensma and I would like to again thank you...

1248
01:47:07,840 --> 01:47:10,510
想要再度感谢你
from the bottom of our hearts.

1249
01:47:10,720 --> 01:47:14,790
不幸地我们没钱再到纽约
Unfortunately, we cannot afford to come to New York again...

1250
01:47:15,000 --> 01:47:18,950
亲自感谢你  不然我们一定会那么做
to thank you in person, or we surely would.

1251
01:47:19,200 --> 01:47:22,030
如果你有机会到匹兹堡
But if you should ever come to Pittsburgh...

1252
01:47:22,320 --> 01:47:26,830
我们非常欢迎你到家里来玩
you would find yourself a most welcome guest in our home.

1253
01:47:27,160 --> 01:47:32,020
非常感激你  柏特与艾薇史提恩斯马
Our deepest thanks, Burt and Ivy Steensma.

